================================================================
B. FIX GHERKIN GRAMMAR  (the file must parse and be sound)
================================================================
- Each scenario must have EXACTLY ONE When (the action under test). If a scenario has two
  distinct actions, split it into two scenarios.
- Assertions belong ONLY in Then. Move any assertion out of Given / When.
- Use "And" / "But" to continue a block; never repeat the Given/When/Then keyword for
