================================================================
G. BACKGROUND
================================================================
- Move a step into Background ONLY if it is a Given that appears in EVERY scenario.
- Background holds Given steps only — never When or Then.
- Do not push a step common to most-but-not-all scenarios into Background.
- Remove Background steps that are then restated inside individual scenarios.

================================================================
